Your task: Implement a recipe sharing community app. Here's what to do:

## 1. Remove template default pages
Delete `Components/Pages/Counter.razor`, `Components/Pages/Weather.razor`, and `Components/Pages/Error.razor`. Keep `Home.razor` but we'll replace its content.

